  "title": "Auditing in Azure SQL Database",
  "contentHtml": "In this special episode Michael talks to prior podcast guest and Azure SQL DB colleague Sravani Saluru&nbsp;\n                     (\n                        <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/sravani-saluru-20012954/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                        <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://twitter.com/sravani_saluru'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-x-twitter\"></i></a>\n                     ) \n                  about how to configure, monitor and manage audit logging in Azure SQL Database. She also shares some inside hints and tips!\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1055720?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1055720/\">SQLLog</a></iframe>\n\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1055720/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-sql-blog/configure-auditing-for-azure-sql-database-series-part1/ba-p/3269758\">Configure Auditing for Azure SQL Database series - Part1</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/azure-sql-blog/configure-auditing-for-azure-sql-database-series-part2/ba-p/3284248\">Configure Auditing for Azure SQL Database series - Part2</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-sql/database/auditing-overview?view=azuresql-db\">Auditing for Azure SQL Database and Azure Synapse Analytics</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/relational-databases/security/auditing/view-a-sql-server-audit-log?view=sql-server-ver16\">View a SQL Server Audit Log</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/relational-databases/system-functions/sys-fn-get-audit-file-transact-sql?view=sql-server-ver16\">sys.fn_get_audit_file</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
